    "bio": "Automation consultant with expertise in n8n, AI models, and workflow optimization. I help educators, startups, and businesses design scalable automation for content creation, exam prep, and process efficiency. Skilled in integrating Google Sheets, Telegram, and AI agents for impactful results.",
